eu_initiatives:
Reference site of the European Innovation Partnership for Active and Healthy Ageing framework. Commitments approved and currently ongoing, that involve FOUND: 
• An integrated Adherence Monitoring System regarding patients with chronic conditions (AG: A1); 
• Getting Optimise Ageing Life-quality: GOAL (AG: A3); 
• Accounting and Information Management System: AIMS (AG: A3); 
• Awareness of Risk of Cardiovascular events in High Risk populations: ARCHR (AG: B3); 
• Assessment of the impact of climate change on senior citizens: ClimAge (AG: D4); 
• Functional foods and microbial components able to improve the wellbeing in older people: FFoAMWeOP (AG: A3); 
• Strategies for the development of new healthy foods for the management of frailty and ageing (NEW AGE FOODS) (AG: A3).
